{"tid":1050602,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"天倫樂優先配屋計劃問題","createTime":"2019-03-07T03:51:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-08T00:00:02.000Z","uid":186628,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"65bc9227aa082807feffb824443f87760785c122","tid":1050602,"uid":186628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T03:51:39.000Z","msg":"因我家有人過左60歲 想申請天倫樂計劃<br />\n但房處會唔會問我同老人家而家住係邊<br />\n因我地同老豆一齊住 但間屋無我地名 咁樣會唔會唔合乎申請?<br />\n因為我有朋友租公屋暗盤 他上年上到水泉澳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b621303c48bdc1bba966f57817021e09b024beb4","tid":1050602,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T03:56:58.000Z","msg":"間屋無名有咩問題先<br />\n朋友/親戚口頭協議租俾你地住<br />\n除非你租公屋暗盤啦<br />\n否則有咩問題"},{"pid":"6a5d04fedfd47624885c0158829b14aaf7bf893a","tid":1050602,"uid":186628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b621303c48bdc1bba966f57817021e09b024beb4","tid":1050602,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T03:56:58.000Z","msg":"間屋無名有咩問題先<br />\n朋友/親戚口頭協議租俾你地住<br />\n除非你租公屋暗盤啦<br />\n否則有咩問題"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T04:08:35.000Z","msg":"多謝清解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我仲有個問題 原本間屋本身有我媽名 但而家要除左佢 除完會唔會有記錄知道佢本身有名？ 會唔會影響到申請？"},{"pid":"1aa4d083e3a064fd347c6f20de123068b3815cd9","tid":1050602,"uid":130695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a5d04fedfd47624885c0158829b14aaf7bf893a","tid":1050602,"uid":186628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b621303c48bdc1bba966f57817021e09b024beb4","tid":1050602,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T03:56:58.000Z","msg":"間屋無名有咩問題先<br />\n朋友/親戚口頭協議租俾你地住<br />\n除非你租公屋暗盤啦<br />\n否則有咩問題"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T04:08:35.000Z","msg":"多謝清解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/a